    <description>TEH 5/18/2022 - UNH Integration - Assigns School of Record based on the Current Program&#39;s Academic Provider

Only triggers this flow when it is changed to &#39;Deposit Received&#39; OR Enrollment Agreement Date/Time field is updated to != null

Accounts for Additional Semester triggering the creation of the Enrollment Record.

Creates an Enrollment Record whenever an Opportunity is Closed Won</description>
